            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Completed my schooling from this school till 12th. As like other students i too felt the same grudge on the adminstration while studying there. But after completing my schooling i really miss the those days of my school life.. Not all teachers are bad here in class 11th and 12th. I got a beautiful set of teachers who made my classes so enjoying and at the same sometimes a little boring which happens. It all depends on ur luck on how teachers come for u.. My PT teachers where also strict as well as way friendly to me, whenever I met them....\nI would suggest guys studying here now to make good memories which last for a lifetime.. I ve got those good memories which I am remembering till now ...\nThanks VVS for giving me a mixed way of studying (strict,Free,Enjoyable) ...\nFor students who are trying to join this wherever u r going to study it's upon you and your will power to shine and I can say Velammal can be a good part of it if u take the opportunities given here",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
